Class InventorySieve

java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.inventory.Inventory
com.rutaji.exaqua.data.recipes.InventorySieve
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.minecraft.inventory.IClearable, net.minecraft.inventory.IInventory, net.minecraft.inventory.IRecipeHelperPopulator
public class InventorySieve extends net.minecraft.inventory.Inventory
Inventory used to comunicate with SieveRecipe and HandSieveRecipe. Stores 1 item, sieve tier, 1 fluid, and it's amount. Used as parametr for CauldronRecipe.matches() and CauldronRecipe.matches(). If used with SieveRecipe tier variable is ignored and is not required.
